# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Syndicate System — .gitignore
# Keeps CODE in the repo; keeps DATA, outputs, and large files OUT.
# Place this file in the o_Automation_Suite folder (the repo root).
# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# ── macOS junk ──
.DS_Store
.AppleDouble
Icon?

# ── Python ──
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*.egg-info/
.ipynb_checkpoints/

# ── Virtual environments ──
venv/
.venv/
env/
.env

# ── Streamlit secrets (never publish) ──
.streamlit/secrets.toml

# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# DATA & GENERATED OUTPUT — do NOT publish (large / regenerated)
# Per-game data can be gigabytes; GitHub rejects files over 100 MB.
# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
Main_Data/
Games/
Variables/
Containers/
Formulas/
Outputs/
debug_html/
logs/

# Registry & caches the app regenerates on its own
clusters.json
**/since_last.json

# Any spreadsheet / database / data file, anywhere in the project
*.csv
*.xlsx
*.xlsm
*.xls
*.accdb
*.mdb

# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Want to publish ONE specific data file (e.g. the rules workbook)?
# After the repo exists, force-add it, e.g.:
#   git add -f Variables/Variable_Elements/Base/f_rules_Gclaude.xlsx
# (In GitHub Desktop: it appears under "ignored" — right-click to include.)
# ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
